                 <td>s (seconds)</td>\n                    </tr>\n                </tbody>\n            </table>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Common Applications</h2>\n            <p>This calculation has applications in:</p>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Physics education: illustrating basic kinematic principles.</li>\n                <li>Engineering: Approximating the impact velocity of falling objects (with caveats about air resistance).</li>\n                <li>Simple simulations:  Providing a basic model for object motion in games or simulations.</li>\n            </ul>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n','\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<style>\n.formula {\n    font-size: 1.2em;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    color: #0056b3;\n    padding: 5px;\n    border: 1px solid #ccc;\n    border-radius: 5px;\n    display: inline-block;\n    background-color: #f0f8ff;\n}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<div class=\"formula\">\n  v = g &times; t\n</div>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n','\n{% extends \'base.html\' %}\n{% block title %} Formula Calculator {% endblock %}\n{% block content %}\n\n<form action=\"{{url_for(\'call\')}}\" method=\"post\" class=\"calculation-form\">\n    <div>\n        <label for=\"g\">Acceleration due to gravity (g) (m/s²):</label>\n        <input type=\"number\" id=\"g\" name=\"g\" placeholder=\"Enter value in m/s²\" step=\"0.01\" min=\"9.7\" max=\"9.9\" required>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <label for=\"t\">Time (t) (s):</label>\n        <input type=\"number\" id=\"t\" name=\"t\" placeholder=\"Enter value in seconds\" step=\"0.01\" min=\"0\" required>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <label for=\"v\">Final velocity (v) (m/s):</label>\n        <input type=\"number\" id=\"v\" name=\"v\" placeholder=\"Enter value in m/s ONLY if known\" step=\"0.01\" >\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"button-group\">\n        <button type=\"submit\" class=\"calculate-btn\">Calculate</button>\n        <button type=\"reset\" class=\"reset-btn\">Reset</button>\n    </div>\n</form>\n\n{% endblock %}\n','\n    # Collect inputs individually\n    g = float(request.form.get(\'g\', 0))\n    t = float(request.form.get(\'t\', 0))\n    v_provided = request.form.get(\'v\')\n\n    # Calculate result\n    result = g * t\n\n    # REQUIRED: Assign to Output with units\n    Output = f\"{result:.2f} m/s\"\n','2025-04-26 16:07:53');
